---
import Layout from './layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Projects</h1>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/AlexGaudon/tallyo" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tallyo</a>
      – My take on a personal finance tracker, since <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intuit_Mint#Shut_down" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Mint</a> ran out of money.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/AlexGaudon/overs.sh" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">overs.sh</a>
      – Super simple file transfer between servers over SSH. Dead easy.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://misery.systems" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">misery.systems</a>
      – Where I mess around with my homelab (yeah, it's really called "misery.systems").
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/AlexGaudon/stocky" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">stocky</a>
      – A Discord bot that spits out stock prices on command.
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/alexgaudon/ntfy-bridge" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ntfy-bridge</a>
      – Bridges Discord and <a href="https://ntfy.sh" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ntfy.sh</a> so you can get notifications wherever you want.
    </li>
  </ul>
</Layout>